name: Cinnamon

reviews.review_text:
We went to this cafe for breakfast and lunch - the food was so tasty and the price was quite cheap (at least coming from the UK)

It is a more international cuisine, but it gave us the break we needed from the Indian dishes.

The watermelon and orange juices were so fresh, the eggs were perfectly cooked, the burgers were big and filling, and the quality was just top!

Additionally, the location is just so pretty - it's like a terrace with a garden and it's beautiful at all times, either during daylight or in the evening.

The service is a bit slow, so if you are in a rush, don't go! But we were on holiday so we didn't care much about that.

This is a lovely little café / restaurant near the crossroads in Benaulim. Very friendly and attentive staff, delicious food and a nice chilled atmosphere. Good music and great to see that they look after stray cats and dogs in the area. Definitely recommended for a bite to eat / drink whilst in Benaulim.

Just Wow!!!
The vibe, the food, the ambiance and the peace. Everything here was amazing and worth visiting. The live music and food is amazing. Interacted with owner, very friendly person and everyone over there were quite friendly and welcoming.

description:
**Cinnamon: A Slice of Culinary Delight in Navelim Camp, Goa**

Nestled in the scenic surroundings of Navelim Camp, Goa, Cinnamon has garnered an impressive rating of 4.1 from nearly 900 enthusiastic patrons. With tags like **"English breakfast"** appearing prominently (25 mentions), along with **"eggs benedict"** (19 mentions) and **"panini"** (11 mentions), this charming café offers a delightful escape into a world of international flavors.

**Ambiance & Design**  
Stepping into Cinnamon is akin to entering a picturesque garden café, where the terrace setting invites you to unwind amidst greenery. The delightful photos reveal a warm and inviting atmosphere, enhanced by airy spaces and artistic décor. Customers have praised the café not only for its pleasant surroundings but also for the tranquil vibe that accompanies the light, upbeat music playing in the background—perfect for enjoying a leisurely meal. One reviewer specifically celebrated how beautiful the venue looks at any time of day, accentuating the café's enchanting appeal. 

**Menu & Culinary Experience**  
The culinary offerings at Cinnamon are varied and enticing, with an emphasis on freshness and quality. Breakfast dishes like the **eggs benedict** and the generous **English breakfast** have earned accolades for their perfect execution. Diners have particularly enjoyed the **watermelon and orange juices**, hailed as refreshingly vibrant complements to their meals. The reviews mention filling **burgers**, highlighting the café's commitment to hearty, satisfying fare. The menu is thoughtfully crafted, catering to both local and international palates, making it an ideal choice for a delightful brunch or lunch break.

**Customer Experience & Service**  
Service at Cinnamon is generally described as friendly and attentive, with staff who go out of their way to ensure a pleasant dining experience. While some have noted that service can be a bit on the slower side—perfectly acceptable for those on holiday—the genuine warmth and hospitality, as emphasized by returning customers, truly stand out. Furthermore, patrons appreciate its welcoming stance towards local stray animals, showcasing the café’s community spirit.

**Popularity & Reviews**  
Cinnamon has established a loyal following, which is evident through the numerous reviews praising its inviting atmosphere and delicious food. The café's reputation as a spot to relax and enjoy breakfast or lunch has resulted in strong word-of-mouth recommendations. Customers frequently mention their satisfaction in both social media posts and review platforms, solidifying Cinnamon's position as a beloved dining destination in Goa. 

**Utilizing Visual Content**  
The provided photographs highlight the appeal of Cinnamon, showing off both the inviting atmosphere and beautifully presented dishes. The garden-like setting and cozy dining area can be seen in the images, making it clear why many choose to linger over their meals and enjoy the peaceful surroundings.

In essence, Cinnamon offers not just a meal, but a delightful experience combining flavorful food, a charming ambiance, and friendly service. Whether it's indulging in an **English breakfast** or savoring a crafted **panini**, this café is a must-visit for anyone exploring the culinary landscape of Navelim Camp in Goa.
